\c 22
\s Ilathi ngaseJordani
\p
\v 1 Ngalesosikhathi uJoshuwa wabiza abakoRubeni labakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sabakoManase,
\v 2 wathi kubo: Lina ligcinile konke uMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* eyalilaya khona\x + Nani 32.20,21,22. Dute.3.18,19,20. Josh. 1.12,13,14,15,16,17.\x*, lalilalela ilizwi lami kukho konke engalilaya khona.
\v 3 Kalibatshiyanga abafowenu kulezinsuku ezinengi, kuze kube lamuhla; kodwa ligcinile imfanelo yomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
\v 4 Khathesi-ke, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ibanikile abafowenu ukuphumula\x + 21.44; 23.1.\x*, njengalokho akukhuluma kubo. Ngakho-ke buyelani lina liye emathenteni enu elizweni lelifa lenu, alinika lona uMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* ngaphetsheya kweJordani\x + 13.8.\x*.
\v 5 Kuphela liqaphelisise ukwenza umlayo lomthetho\x + Dute. 6.6,17; 11.22.\x* uMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* alilaya wona, ukuthanda\x + Dute. 6.5; 10.12.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, lokuhamba endleleni zayo zonke, lokugcina imilayo yayo, lokunamathela\x + 23.8. Dute. 10.20.\x* kuyo, lokuyikhonza ngenhliziyo yenu yonke langomphefumulo wenu wonke.
\v 6 Wasebabusisa\x + 22.7; 14.13. Eks. 39.43.\x* uJoshuwa ebayekela behamba, baya emathenteni abo.
\v 7 Njalo kungxenye yesizwe sakoManase uMozisi wayenike \add indawo\add* eBashani; kodwa kungxenye yayo uJoshuwa wayinika \add indawo\add* labafowabo nganeno kweJordani\x + 17.5.\x* entshonalanga. Njalo-ke nxa uJoshuwa ebayekela behamba besiya emathenteni abo, wababusisa.
\v 8 Wakhuluma labo esithi: Buyelani emathenteni enu lilenotho\x + 2 Lan. 1.11,12.\x* enengi lezifuyo ezinengi kakhulu lilesiliva legolide lethusi lensimbi lezigqoko ezinengi kakhulu; lehlukaniselane\x + 1 Sam. 30.24. Nani 31.27.\x* impango yezitha zenu labafowenu.
\p
\v 9 Abantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase basebebuyela, besuka ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli bephuma eShilo\x + 18.1.\x* eselizweni leKhanani, ukuya elizweni leGileyadi\x + Nani 32.1,26,29.\x*, elizweni lelifa labo ababelizuzile, ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* ngesandla sikaMozisi.
\v 10 Kwathi sebefikile emingceleni yeJordani eselizweni leKhanani, abantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase bakha khona ilathi ngaseJordani, ilathi elikhulu ngokubonakala.
\p
\v 11 Kwathi abantwana bakoIsrayeli besizwa kuthiwa\x + Dute. 13.12,13,14,15. Hlu. 20.12.\x*: Khangelani, abantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase bakhile ilathi maqondana lelizwe leKhanani emingceleni eJordani ehlangothini lwabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 12 Kwathi abantwana bakoIsrayeli be\add ku\add*zwa, inhlangano yonke\x + Hlu. 20.1.\x* yabantwana bakoIsrayeli yabuthana eShilo ukwenyukela kubo empini.
\v 13 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebethuma kubantwana bakoRubeni\x + Dute. 13.12,13,14,15. Hlu. 20.12.\x* lakubantwana bakoGadi lengxenyeni eyodwa kwezimbili yesizwe sakoManase elizweni leGileyadi uPhinehasi indodana kaEleyazare\x + Nani 25.7.\x* umpristi,
\v 14 lezinduna ezilitshumi laye, induna eyodwa ngendlu ngayinye yaboyise ivela kuzo zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli; ngayinye yayiyinhloko yendlu yaboyise\x + Nani 1.4.\x*, kunkulungwane zakoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 15 Basebefika kubantwana bakoRubeni lakubantwana bakoGadi lengxenyeni eyodwa kwezimbili yesizwe sakoManase elizweni leGileyadi, bakhuluma labo besithi:
\v 16 Itsho njalo inhlangano yonke yeN\nd kosi\nd*: Kuyisiphambeko bani eseliphambeke ngaso limelane loNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, liphambuka lamuhla ekuyilandeleni iN\nd kosi\nd*, ekuzakheleni ilathi, ukuze lihlamukele\x + Nani 14.9. Josh. 22.19. Levi 17.8,9. Dute. 12.13,14.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* lamuhla?
\v 17 Ngabe isiphambeko sePeyori\x + Nani 23.28.\x* sincinyane kakhulu kithi yini, esingahlanjululwanga kuso kuze kube lamuhla, lanxa inhlupheko yayiphakathi kwenhlangano yeN\nd kosi\nd*,
\v 18 ukuze lina liphenduke lamuhla ekuyilandeleni iN\nd kosi\nd*? Kuzakuthi uba lina liyihlamuka\x + Nani 14.9. Josh. 22.19. Levi 17.8,9. Dute. 12.13,14.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* lamuhla, kusasa izayithukuthelela inhlangano yonke\x + 22.20. Nani 16.22.\x* yakoIsrayeli.
\v 19 Kodwa ngeqiniso, uba ilizwe lemfuyo yenu lingcolile, chaphelani lina elizweni lemfuyo yeN\nd kosi\nd* lapho ithabhanekele leN\nd kosi\nd* elihlala khona\x + 18.1.\x*, lizizuzele imfuyo phakathi kwethu; kodwa lingayihlamukeli\x + Nani 14.9. Josh. 22.19. Levi 17.8,9. Dute. 12.13,14.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* njalo lingasihlamukeli ekuzakheleni kwenu ilathi ngaphandle kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu.
\v 20 UAkani indodana kaZera kaphambekanga yini ngesiphambeko entweni eqalekisiweyo\x + 7.1,5.\x*, kwasekusiba lolaka phezu kwenhlangano yonke yakoIsrayeli? Leyondoda kayibhubhanga-ke yodwa esiphambekweni sayo.
\p
\v 21 Abantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi lengxenye yesizwe sakoManase basebephendula bathi kunhloko zezinkulungwane zakoIsrayeli:
\v 22 UNkulunkulu wabonkulunkulu\x + Dute. 10.17.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wabonkulunkulu, iN\nd kosi\nd*, uyazi\x + Jobe 10.7; 23.10. Hlab. 44.20,21. Jer. 12.3. 2 Kor. 11.11,31.\x*, loIsrayeli kakwazi; uba bekungokuhlamuka kumbe uba ngokuphambuka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lingasisindisi lamuhla,
\v 23 ukuthi sizakhele ilathi ukuphambuka ekuyilandeleni iN\nd kosi\nd*, loba sinikelele phezu kwalo umnikelo wokutshiswa loba umnikelo wokudla, loba ukwenza phezu kwalo iminikelo yokuthula, iN\nd kosi\nd* uqobo kayikudinge\x + 1 Sam. 20.16. Dute. 18.19.\x*.
\v 24 Kodwa ngeqiniso sikwenze ngokunqineka nga\add lolu\add*daba sisithi: Kusasa abantwana benu bazakhuluma kubantwana bethu bathi: Lilani leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli?
\v 25 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* iyenzile iJordani yaba ngumngcele phakathi kwethu lani, \add lina\add* bantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi, kalilasabelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni. Ngalokho abantwana benu benze abantwana bethu ukuthi bayekele ukuyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 26 Ngakho sathi: Kasizilungiseleni khathesi ukwakha ilathi, lingabi ngelomnikelo wokutshiswa, njalo lingabi ngelomhlatshelo,
\v 27 kodwa libe yibufakazi\x + 22.28,34; 24.27\x* phakathi kwethu lani lezizukulwana zethu emva kwethu, ukuthi sikhonze inkonzo yeN\nd kosi\nd* phambi kwayo ngeminikelo yethu yokutshiswa\x + Dute. 12.5,6,11,12,17,18,26,27.\x* langemihlatshelo yethu langeminikelo yethu yokuthula, ukuze abantwana benu bangathi ebantwaneni bethu kusasa: Kalilasabelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 28 Sasesisithi: Kuzakuthi-ke, nxa bekhuluma \add lokhu\add* kithi lesizukulwaneni sethu kusasa, sizakuthi: Bonani umfanekiso\x + Dute. 4.16.\x* welathi leN\nd kosi\nd* obaba abalakhayo, kungeyisilo lomnikelo wokutshiswa lingeyisilo lomhlatshelo, kodwa liyibufakazi phakathi kwethu lani.
\v 29 Kakube khatshana lathi ukuthi siyihlamuke iN\nd kosi\x + 22.16,18,19,22.\x*\nd*, lokuthi siphenduke lamuhla ekuyilandeleni iN\nd kosi\nd*, ukwakha ilathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa lelomnikelo wokudla lelomhlatshelo, ngaphandle kwelathi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu eliphambi kwethabhanekele layo.
\p
\v 30 Kwathi uPhinehasi\x + 22.13,14.\x* umpristi lenduna zenhlangano lenhloko zezinkulungwane zakoIsrayeli ezazilaye bewezwa amazwi abantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi labantwana bakoManase abawakhulumayo, kwakukuhle emehlweni abo.
\v 31 UPhinehasi indodana kaEleyazare umpristi wasesithi kubantwana bakoRubeni lakubantwana bakoGadi lakubantwana bakoManase: Lamuhla siyazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* iphakathi kwethu\x + Levi 26.11,12.\x*, ngoba kaliphambekanga lesisiphambeko eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; khathesi likhulule abantwana bakoIsrayeli esandleni seN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 32 UPhinehasi indodana kaEleyazare umpristi lezinduna basebebuyela bevela ebantwaneni bakoRubeni lebantwaneni bakoGadi elizweni leGileyadi\x + 22.10,11,15.\x*, besiya elizweni leKhanani ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli, babuyisela ilizwi kubo.
\v 33 Lodaba lwaluluhle emehlweni abantwana bakoIsrayeli; abantwana bakoIsrayeli bambusisa uNkulunkulu\x + 1 Lan. 29.20. Neh. 8.6. Dan. 2.19. Luka 2.28.\x*, kabasakhulumanga \add ngo\add*kwenyukela kubo empini ukuchitha ilizwe abantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi ababehlala kulo.
\v 34 Abantwana bakoRubeni labantwana bakoGadi balibiza ilathi ngokuthi: Liyibufakazi phakathi kwethu bokuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* inguNkulunkulu\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*.
